Class BufferingMap<K,E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • bt.BufferingMap<K,E>
  • Type Parameters:
    K - Key type
    E - Collection element type

    public class BufferingMap<K,E>
extends Object
    Convenient utility class to create maps, that act as temporary buffers for storing values between their initial collection and retrieval for further processing. Thread-safe.
    Since:
    1.6
